    "content": "<h2>Sluneční soustava</h2>\n<p><strong>Sluneční soustava</strong> se skládá ze Slunce a všech těles, která kolem něj obíhají.</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 480 120' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'>\n  <circle cx='30' cy='60' r='22' fill='#fef3c7' stroke='#f59e0b' stroke-width='2'/><text x='30' y='65' text-anchor='middle' font-size='12'>☀</text>\n  <circle cx='70' cy='60' r='3' fill='#9ca3af' opacity='0.7'/><text x='70' y='77' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='8'>Me</text><circle cx='95' cy='60' r='5' fill='#f59e0b' opacity='0.7'/><text x='95' y='79' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='8'>V</text><circle cx='125' cy='60' r='5' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.7'/><text x='125' y='79' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='8'>Z</text><circle cx='155' cy='60' r='4' fill='#ef4444' opacity='0.7'/><text x='155' y='78' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='8'>Ma</text><circle cx='210' cy='60' r='14' fill='#f59e0b' opacity='0.7'/><text x='210' y='88' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='8'>Ju</text><circle cx='280' cy='60' r='12' fill='#eab308' opacity='0.7'/><text x='280' y='86' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='8'>Sa</text><circle cx='340' cy='60' r='8' fill='#93c5fd' opacity='0.7'/><text x='340' y='82' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='8'>U</text><circle cx='400' cy='60' r='7' fill='#3b82f6' opacity='0.7'/><text x='400' y='81' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='8'>N</text>\n  <circle cx='280' cy='60' rx='12' fill='none' stroke='#eab308' stroke-width='1'/>\n  <line x1='265' y1='55' x2='295' y2='55' stroke='#eab308' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <text x='240' y='110' text-anchor='middle' fill='#6b7280' font-size='9'>kamenné planety | plynní a ledoví obři</text>\n  <line x1='180' y1='100' x2='180' y2='95' stroke='#6b7280' stroke-width='1'/>\n</svg></div><h3>Planety (od Slunce)</h3>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Planeta</th><th>Typ</th><th>Průměr (km)</th><th>Vzdálenost od Slunce</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>Merkur</td><td>kamenná</td><td>4 879</td><td>0,39 AU</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Venuše</td><td>kamenná</td><td>12 104</td><td>0,72 AU</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Země</td><td>kamenná</td><td>12 756</td><td>1 AU</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Mars</td><td>kamenná</td><td>6 792</td><td>1,52 AU</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Jupiter</td><td>plynný obr</td><td>142 984</td><td>5,20 AU</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Saturn</td><td>plynný obr</td><td>120 536</td><td>9,54 AU</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Uran</td><td>ledový obr</td><td>51 118</td><td>19,2 AU</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Neptun</td><td>ledový obr</td><td>49 528</td><td>30,1 AU</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p><strong>1 AU</strong> (astronomická jednotka) ≈ 150 milionů km (vzdálenost Země–Slunce).</p>"
  }
}
